    note: 
  notes: 'Level adi: Level_22

    Boyut: 26x15

    Zorluk: Renk hazirlama

    Mekanik
    ozeti: Red button, Blue pressure plate ve Purple button ile renk hazirlama yan
    yollari. Donus looplari eklendi.

    Start koordinati: (2,12)

    Goal koordinati:
    (24,3)

    Renkli kilitler: YellowButton (6,10) link=R22 face=Blue; YellowButton
    (18,7) link=P22 face=Purple; YellowDoor (21,3) link=P22 face=Purple; YellowDoor
    (11,8) link=R22 face=Blue

    PressurePlate requiredFace bilgisi: (13,12) requiredFace=Red,
    mode=ActivateOnly, singleUse=False

    ToggleBridge bilgisi: (16,10) link=B22,
    startsActive=False

    OneTimeTile koordinatlari: Yok

    IceSlide rotalari:
    Yok

    GreenJump ve JumpLanding koordinatlari: Jump Yok; Landing Yok

    RedBreakable
    koordinatlari: Yok

    Gelistirici test cozum rotasi: Right, Right, Right, Right,
    Down, Down, Down, Down, Right, Right, Right, Right, Up, Up, Up, Up, Right, Right,
    Right, Right, Down, Down, Down, Down, Down, Right, Right, Right, Right, Right,
    Down, Down, Down, Down, Right, Right, Right, Right, Right

'
